{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"131-babachya-mishya","title":"बाबाच्या मिश्या","description":"अनूला बाबाचं सगळ्यात जास्त काय आवडतं, तर त्याच्या मिश्या.\r\nखरं म्हणजे तिला मिश्यावाली सगळीच माणसं आवडतात.\r\nमिश्या बघितल्या की तिला काय काय भन्नाट कल्पना सुचतात.\r\n","language":"Marathi","langCode":"mr","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Madhuri Purandare"],"illustrators":["Madhuri Purandare"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/131-babachya-mishya"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721686/size3/0eaa2e9b2d4d4c465ba2c5e05a6f092c.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721686/size6/0eaa2e9b2d4d4c465ba2c5e05a6f092c.jpg"},"audio":{"src":"https://storage.googleapis.com/story-weaver-e2e-production/stories/131/audios/story/131-babachya-mishya.mp3","cues":[[1,0,2.04],[2,2.04,2.48],[3,2.48,3.88],[4,3.88,4.36],[5,4.36,4.84],[6,4.84,6.4],[7,6.4,6.92],[8,6.92,7.52],[9,7.52,9.24],[10,9.24,9.48],[11,9.48,10.44],[12,10.44,11.32],[13,11.32,12.48],[14,12.48,12.92],[15,12.92,13.32],[16,13.32,14.4],[17,14.4,16.56],[18,16.56,17.44],[19,17.44,17.8],[20,17.8,18.04],[21,18.04,18.44],[22,18.44,18.76],[23,18.76,20.08],[24,20.08,20.88],[25,20.88,21.88],[26,21.88,23],[27,23,23.56],[28,23.56,24.12],[29,24.12,24.44],[30,24.44,25.56],[31,25.56,25.96],[32,25.96,27.42],[33,27.42,27.8],[34,27.8,28.72],[35,28.72,29.4],[36,29.4,31.6],[37,31.6,32.2],[38,32.2,32.44],[39,32.44,33.28],[40,33.28,33.48],[41,33.48,34.36],[42,34.36,35.92],[43,35.92,37.12],[44,37.12,38.56],[45,38.56,39.64],[46,39.64,40.24],[47,40.24,41.16],[48,41.16,41.84],[49,41.84,43.28],[50,43.28,43.92],[51,43.92,44.56],[52,44.56,45.4],[53,45.4,46.2],[54,46.2,46.36],[55,46.36,46.88],[56,46.88,48.8